(7, 11, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;插件网站：<a href=\\"http://malsup.com/jquery/block/#demos\\" target=\\"_blank\\">http://malsup.com/jquery/block/#demos</a></p>\r\n<p>编码时出现最大问题是在弹出层上多次切换登录和注册按钮，再点关闭，再重新点页面上的按钮时，弹出层就怎么都弹不出来了。最终答案是：关闭按钮要写在onUnblock回调函数里面；</p>\r\n<p>附上示例代码（也即本站的登录和注册特效）：</p>\r\n<p>&lt;div class=&quot;login user_wrap&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;login-form&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control login-field&quot; value=&quot;&quot; placeholder=&quot;用户名&quot; id=&quot;username&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;label class=&quot;login-field-icon fui-user&quot; for=&quot;username&quot;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;password&quot; class=&quot;form-control login-field&quot; value=&quot;&quot; placeholder=&quot;密码&quot; id=&quot;password&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;label class=&quot;login-field-icon fui-lock&quot; for=&quot;password&quot;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a class=&quot;btn btn-success btn-lg btn-user s_login&quot; href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot;&gt;登陆&lt;/a&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a class=&quot;btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-user s_reg&quot; href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot;&gt;注册&lt;/a&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a class=&quot;btn btn-close&quot; href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot;&gt;关闭&lt;/a&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&lt;div class=&quot;clear&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&lt;div class=&quot;reg user_wrap&quot; style=&quot;di