ou\\''re with your friends and starting digging into the mayo.</div>\r\n    <div class=\\"clearall\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\\"stepedit\\" style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 20px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; list-style: none; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); clear: both; position: relative;\\">\r\n    <div class=\\"mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter \\" style=\\"margin: -21px -21px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; max-width: 670px;\\"><a href=\\"http://www.wikihow.com/Play-a-Prank#/Image:Play-a-Prank-Step-7-Version-2.jpg\\" class=\\"image lightbox\\" data-href=\\"/Image:Play-a-Prank-Step-7-Version-2.jpg?ajax=true\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 102, 51); text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word; display: block; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgb(223, 223, 223); border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px;\\"><img alt=\\"Play a Prank Step 7 Version 2.jpg\\" src=\\"http://pad1.whstatic.com/images/thumb/d/d0/Play-a-Prank-Step-7-Version-2.jpg/670px-Play-a-Prank-Step-7-Version-2.jpg\\" id=\\"55e4c977a3503\\" data-src=\\"http://pad1.whstatic.com/images/thumb/d/d0/Play-a-Prank-Step-7-Version-2.jpg/670px-Play-a-Prank-Step-7-Version-2.jpg\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 667px; height: auto;\\" /></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\\"step_num\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 15px 3px 0px; font-size: 43px; float: left; font-weight: bold;\\">7</div>\r\n    <div class=\\"step\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\"><b class=\\"whb\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">Switch the salt and the sugar.</b>&nbsp;Put sugar in the salt shaker and put salt in the sugar bowl (or even in the sugar bag).</div>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div id=\\"steps_1\\" class=