er;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">YOUR COUNTRY</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Which country are you from?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Where is this country located?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Which part of the country do most people live in?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What are the main industries in your country?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Is it easy to travel around your country?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">CLOTHES</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What type of clothes do you like to wear?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of clothes do people in your country usually wear?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">How important is fashion to you?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of clothes do you dislike?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you think people behave differently in different kinds of clothes?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of clothes do people wear to work in your country?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Are clothes expensive in your country?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">GOING OUT</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you like going out or staying at home?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What do you like to do when you go out?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">How often do you go out?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do people in your country go out a lot?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">How and where do people in your country usually socialize?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of entertainment is popular in your country?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">GAMES</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you enjoy playing any games?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of games do you play?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you think adults should play games?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What do children learn from games?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of games did you play when you were a child?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What games are popular in your country today?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of games were popular when you were young?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you think mental games like chess are good for you?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">COLOURS</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you have a favourite colour?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What are your country&rsquo;s colours?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you think colours affect our moods?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Can you learn anything about a person from the colours he / she likes?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you like the same colours now as you did when you were a child?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">MUSIC</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you like music?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of music do you like?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">When do you usually listen to music?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of music did you like when you were younger?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">What kind of music is popular in your country?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you play any musical instruments?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Do you wish you could play any musical instruments?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">Which is your favourite instrument?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">source url: </span><a href=\\"http://www.goodluckielts.com/IELTS-speaking-topics.html\\" target=\\"_blank\\"><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\">http://www.goodluckielts.com/IELTS-speaking-topics.html</span></a></p>'),
(120, 20, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p>Question: How could I improve my voice?</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Answer: Get a small tape recorder and analyze your voice first. If you don\\''t like it, work at it.</div>\r\n<div>Most professional entertainers and even myself visit a voice coach. <span style=\\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\\">One exercise he gave me to deepen my voice was to say &quot;la-lay-lee-low-lu; la-lay-lee-low-lu; la-lay-lee-low-lu&quot;</span> You can do that anywhere you are even in a boardroom. Just be sure the president doesn\\''t walk in.</div>\r\n<div>Try to have an assertive voice, not a domineering one, but assertive. There is a difference. You might get introduced to somebody with a very domineering voice and that would sound like, &quot;My name is Sylvester! (Get it right or I\\''ll kill you!)&quot; And you don\\''t like that too much.</div>\r\n<div>And then we have people with very soft voices, and on top they end a sentence with a question mark, &quot;My name is Peter. I think it is, isn\\''t it?&quot; Now both are not what I want you to be. I would like you to project in a firm, concise and assertive voice on your next presentation.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>我该如何改善发音呢？</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>先用一个小型录音机来分析你的嗓音。如果不喜欢，你就要加以改善。</div>\r\n<div>大多数专业喜剧演员,包括我, 都有声音教练。他教我一个方法可以使声音变得更深沉, 说 &ldquo;啦莱哩喽噜，啦莱哩喽噜，啦莱哩喽噜&rdquo;.你可以在任何地方进行练习, 甚至可以在会议室.只不过要确定总裁那时候不在。</div>\r\n<div>尽量使用自信的语气，不是嚣张的语气，而是自信。这两者是截然不同的。你可能听过有些人语气嚣张地自我介绍说：&ldquo;我是西尔维斯特！（听清楚了，否则我杀了你！）&rdquo;你肯定不会喜欢的。</div>\r\n<div>而有的人则说话软弱无力，说每句话都带着问号:&ldquo;我名叫彼得。我想应该是这样,对吧？&rdquo; 以上都不是我所希望你拥有的,你应该在下场演讲上展示你坚定、凝练和自信的嗓音。</div>');
